\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng Tam s\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh b\u1ecb Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia 4-3 sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m (120 ph\u00fat c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 h\u00f2a 1-1) t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Tam s\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau lo\u1ea1t \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d c\u00e2n n\u00e3o t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1996 t\u1edbi nay v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Jose <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh-421-190394.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh</span>. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Tam s\u01b0. Mourinho b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/hau-ve-Trippier.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTrippier ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 penalty th\u1ee9 4 trong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. \u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\u201d, Trippier n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKi\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y Colombia c\u00f3 20 t\u1edbi 25 ph\u00fat l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt. \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u theo \u00fd m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u1eb1m xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ri\u00eang v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Henderson (b\u1ecb Barrios h\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u) v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ecd ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Colombia. \u1ede c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\">T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-chan-thuong-cua-vardy-421-190385.html\">\u0110T Anh c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-southgate-va-niem-tin-mu-quang-vao-raheem-sterling-421-190376.html\">\u0110T Anh: Southgate v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng v\u00e0o Raheem Sterling</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"932","checkdouble":"190462"},{"date":"06:58 06/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p lo ng\u1ea1i DNA ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/nguoi-phap-lo-ngai-dna-phong-ngu-cua-uruguay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao Edinson Cavani c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Deschamps chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o cho Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay 21h, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Uruguay. Thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Edinson Cavani c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Cavani c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng Deschamps tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Oscar Tabarez c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/tien-dao-Cavani.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cavani c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Cavani ra s\u00e2n\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 49 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cNh\u01b0ng HLV Tabarez c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Stuani c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e3 ghi 21 b\u00e0n cho CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua (Girona). T\u00f4i c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c nhau trong \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Cavani. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf Ph\u00e1p (cho PSG), t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Cavani l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba nh\u01b0ng Stuani r\u1ed3i Rodriguez c\u0169ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Didier Deschamps\" title=\"Didier Deschamps\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Phap-bat-tay-Dan-Mach-hoa-nhat-Dieu-ru-ngu-o-Luzhniki-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lo ng\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a 0-0 v\u1edbi Uruguay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Deschamps n\u0103m 2012. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf 4 trong 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau. Deschamps c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng so s\u00e1nh hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 6 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong DNA c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Deschamps n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nam M\u1ef9, h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u1ea7n v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, c\u00e1nh tay c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn. Khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\">Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng mang t\u00ean Pogbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/torreira-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-uruguay-vs-phap-421-190425.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\">Trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-uruguay-se-ha-phap-ma-khong-can-cavani-421-190310.html\">Suarez: Uruguay s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 Ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cavani</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/wenger-tuyen-anh-se-tranh-cup-vang-voi-phap-va-brazil-421-190292.html\">Wenger: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Brazil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"931","checkdouble":"190463"},{"date":"15:59 05/07","title":"\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e2y k\u00edn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/dt-nhat-ban-duoc-chao-don-nhu-nhung-nguoi-hung-du-bi-loai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0ng tr\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay Narita (Chiba) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<h2>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc:</h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/Wild-scenes-at-Narita-Airport-as-Samurai-Blue-returns-home\uff1aThe-Asahi-Shimbun.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><br>\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n<div>Sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng m\u00e1y bay v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng 5/7 (theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng). D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng khi c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 800 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n bay Narita (Chiba) \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/dt-nhat-ban-duoc-chao-don-nhu-nhung-nguoi-hung-du-bi-loai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n khi xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \"samurai xanh\", qu\u00e2y k\u00edn l\u1ed1i \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n khi xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ea3nh s\u00e2n bay. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Akira Nishino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng v\u00e2y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c l\u00e0 NHM Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng chen l\u1ea5n, x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>M\u1ed9t ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Setagaya Ward (Tokyo) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n bay t\u1eeb \u0111\u00eam h\u00f4m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng khi Keisuke Honda ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\"T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n h\u00e9t l\u1edbn l\u00ean 'c\u1ea3m \u01a1n' v\u00e0 'c\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t'.\"<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, hai l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2002 v\u00e0 2010. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \"samurai xanh\" \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9 hai b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 Keisuke Honda (32 tu\u1ed5i) v\u00e0 Makoto Hasebe (34 tu\u1ed5i) \u0111\u1ec1u tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190297.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-tiet-lo-su-khac-biet-cua-dt-bi-421-190265.html\">Hazard ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/nhat-ban-roi-world-cup-2018-tieng-vong-tu-chau-a-466-190253.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chia tay World Cup 2018: Ti\u1ebfng v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-nhat-ban-thua-bi-465-190248.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/suyt-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-bi-nhat-ban-lap-ky-luc-world-cup-465-190240.html\">Su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"930","checkdouble":"190430"},{"date":"16:18 05/07","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, Luciano Moggi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf xong xu\u00f4i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro d\u00e0nh cho Cristiano Ronaldo. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a 2017/18, c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, trong 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Ronaldo lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Madrid. V\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, Juventus r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a CR7. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juve s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span> t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Moggi-tiet-lo-Ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLuciano Moggi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2006. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, d\u1ef1a theo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u00f4ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Juventus t\u1ea1i Munich\u201d, Moggi n\u00f3i tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Italia, Tele7Gold. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 trong \u0111\u1ea7u sau khi n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eebng \u201cv\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t\u201d Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Moggi t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Ronaldo tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus n\u0103m 2002. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Sporting Lisbon song \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo chuan bi chuyen toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo chuan bi chuyen toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMoggi t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Marcelo Salas di chuy\u1ec3n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i song b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, CR7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Manchester United v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2003. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean\u201d, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Juve n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi quan s\u00e1t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i song \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, Marcelo Salas \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sporting Lisbon v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i River Plate. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-va-messi-dat-tay-nhau-ve-nuoc-doan-ket-cuoc-hanh-trinh-421-190180.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-messi-la-ronaldo-cua-dt-anh-421-190088.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 Messi, l\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-bo-dao-nha-465-190053.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"929","checkdouble":"190431"},{"date":"16:31 05/07","title":"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-luc-luong-cua-dt-anh-truoc-tran-gap-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tiki-taka l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn cho La Roja kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n xa. Nh\u01b0ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u00ec 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</h2><h2>Koke</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u1ea1nh Sergio Busquets \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 La Roja. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-o-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Koke ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKoke \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Koke ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a anh thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i t\u00ednh s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Koke v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Nga c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. T\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n, c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Koke kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Akinfeev \u0111\u1ea9y ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Koke \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Silva\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva\" title=\"David Silva\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162516-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>David Silva tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Silva l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a Man City l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh Premier League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a La Roja trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, David Silva \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018. Anh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Silva v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Iran nh\u01b0ng anh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, David Silva l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo;. Anh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nga l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. D\u1eabu cho v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng David Silva kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0o l\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra s\u1edbm b\u1edfi l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Iniesta trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David De Gea\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162625-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>De Gea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Gea l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi tranh, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. C\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ed7ng nhi\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi De Gea b\u1eaft h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng y h\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1edf World Cup, De Gea c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t. Trong s\u1ed1 7 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 penalty n\u00e0o \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1edbi Nga. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 De Gea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t De Gea xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap La Roja ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-co-the-dan-dat-tay-ban-nha-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190427.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi-421-190397.html\">K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"928","checkdouble":"190432"},{"date":"17:02 05/07","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-vu-sao-khung-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Sevilla thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emirates.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Ever Banega\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Mirror v\u00e0 ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m Ever Banega c\u1ee7a Sevilla.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Kha-nang-Arsenal-mua-Ever-Banega-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Banega</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Sevilla v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi 51 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBanega l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Sevilla c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Banega t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Sevilla</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Sevilla thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal muon mua Banega\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Banega\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Arsenal-muon-mua-Ever-Banega-cua-Sevilla-voi-gia-25-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Banega tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Sevilla</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Banega cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Sevilla nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Banega, Arsenal c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Steven N'Zonzi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"927","checkdouble":"190433"},{"date":"17:09 05/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/truoc-vong-tu-ket-tam-su-don-nhan-vien-binh-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ea1c quan, khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Fabian Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2>Delph \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p HLV Gareth Southgate v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00ea&rdquo;. Theo \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ee3 anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sinh \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 3, v\u00e0 Fabian Delph \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc chuy\u00ean c\u01a1, gi\u00fap anh ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ec3u c\u00f4ng ch\u00faa ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi trong s\u1ef1 m\u1eebng r\u1ee1. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua 24 gi\u1edd tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ecdi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng trong nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0o l\u00fac 7:52 s\u00e1ng, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng 2 c\u00f4 con g\u00e1i xinh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 n\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; &ndash; Fabian Delph chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau khi \u0111\u00f3n con g\u00e1i th\u1ee9 3\" title=\"Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau khi \u0111\u00f3n con g\u00e1i th\u1ee9 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/delph.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau khi \u0111\u00f3n con g\u00e1i th\u1ee9 3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Delph \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed wingback c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm d\u00f9 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd cho HLV Gareth Southgate th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Tam S\u01b0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ashley Young \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, v\u00e0 Danny Rose l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng, nh\u01b0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia v\u1eeba qua. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Fabian Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa s\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n &ndash; m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\">T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng ai quan t\u00e2m, \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Ket-qua-Colombia-vs-Anh-tran-dau-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 bi k\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd v\u00e0 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u00fat h\u1ecfng (c\u1ea7n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"926","checkdouble":"190434"}]}